  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To address the preemptive analgesic effect of preoperative gabapentoids versus no&#xD;
      gabapentoids in orthopedic surgery&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Computer search for all studies used preoperative gabapentoids versus no gabapentoids in&#xD;
      orthopedic surgery during the last 10 years (from 2011 - 2020)&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
